title: [There's No Place Like Home]
description: Polished oak supports carved with a rose and vine pattern peak the tent ceiling in two places.  Lanterns hang from each slender pillar shedding a pale light over the room.  Brightly colored rugs line the floor creating a mosaic in a wide array of blues.  Standing in one corner of the space is a a large mistwood sign.
location: between Wehnimer's Landing and Zul Logoth
